    "Our methodology consisted of a range of different elements.",
    "In line with best practices in life cycle assessment 14, we engaged with the following four stages: goal and scope, inventory analysis, impact assessment, and interpretation.",
    "The goal of this research effort is to compare AI writing and illustration with human writing and illustration.",
    "As will most life cycle assessment processes, it is impossible to include every item and process that has some bearing on the phenomena being studied (e.g., the food eaten by the instructor who taught one of the software engineers about AI, or the car driven by the English teacher who taught the person to write).",
